## Goal of this notebook

Importing and cleaning weather data for analysis.

```{r}
#| label: setup
#| message: false
#| warning: false

library(tidyverse)
library(janitor)
```

## Import

Importing the weather data into the project. 

```{r}
#| label: import

weather <- read_csv("data-original/weather.csv")

weather |> glimpse()
```

## Clean columns

Cleaning the columns and column names.

```{r}
weather <- weather |>
  clean_names() |>
  select(!c(tavg, tobs))

weather |> glimpse()
```

## Export

Exporting the cleaned data as rds.

```{r}
#| label: export

write_rds(
  weather,
  "data-processed/01-weather-cleaned.rds"
)
```

